Revision history for Tickit-Widget-Progressbar

0.101     2014-08-16 03:29:00+01:00 Europe/London
	No new features

	Dependency fixes:
	* Tickit::Widget

0.100     2013-09-08 19:21:20 Europe/London
	Features:
	* Switched to Tickit::RenderBuffer
	* Helper method to expose only the areas that need drawing
	(currently disabled pending tests to prove that it's doing
	the right thing)
	* Style support
	* Initial support for gradients, currently disabled since
	it would require the Tickit::Colour mapping code which is
	not yet on CPAN.

0.002     2011-12-04 22:30:31 Europe/London
	Fix abstract, update documentation

0.001     2011-11-27 05:43:39 Europe/London
	Initial CPAN release
